<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrīgaṇādhipatayē namaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> namastuṁgaśiraścuṁbicaṁdracāmaracāravē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>
<lb n="2"/>trailōkyanagarāraṁbhamūlastaṁbhāya śaṁbhavē <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrījayābhyudaya śakavaruṣa
<lb n="3"/>1345 neya varttamāna śōbhakrutsaṁvatsarada caitra śu 1 Ālu śrīmadrājādhi
<lb n="4" break="no"/>rāja rājaparamēśvara śrīpatāpa vijayabhūpatirāyamahārāyara sā(ṁ)mrā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>jyābhyudayakāladalu Avara Āgṅādhārakarumappa śrīmanmahāpradhāna baice
<lb n="6" break="no"/>daṁṇāyakaOḍeyara nirūpadiṁ nāgaṁṇagaḷu maṁgalūrarājyava pratipālisuva kāla
<lb n="7" break="no"/>dalu Ā vijayabhūpatirāyamahārāyarige Āyuṣyābhivṛ
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ddhi Ahaṁtāgi durggādēviya japanimittavāgi śrītimirēśvaradē
<lb n="9" break="no"/>varalu yibaru brāhmaṇara kayyalu durggāparamēśvariya japava māḍi
<lb n="10" break="no"/>sa Āyiba<note n="87-4">The rest of the inscription is covered by the pedestal of the image.</note>
</p>

